VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'over. You tweak the prompt, you try a different model, you burn 20 minutes before you have even written a single line of code. We have all been there.'

[01:39] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'With multi-plan mode, you do not pick a model at all. You just tell Verdin what you want to build. And Verdin automatically calls in three top-tier models, Opus 4.6,'

[01:52] [scene:talk]
